{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Setting this property to "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" causes the map view to use the Core Location"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"framework to find the current location. As long as this property is "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view continues to track the user’s location and update it periodically."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property does not indicate whether the user’s position is actually visible"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on the map, only whether the map view is allowed to display it. To determine"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whether the user’s position is visible, use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocationVisible"},{"type":"text","text":" property."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Your app must specify a value for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription"},{"type":"text","text":" or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription"},{"type":"text","text":" 